{"tid":876753,"cid":13,"subCid":0,"title":"女友代男友出售高達模型、四驅車","createTime":"2018-10-26T00:17:31.000Z","updateTime":"2018-10-26T05:56:07.000Z","uid":81228,"like":1,"dislike":7,"uniUserReply":23,"replies":[{"pid":"e1c8b3c67203a820c999df280214fd87cf6d05ae","tid":876753,"uid":81228,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2018-10-26T00:17:31.000Z","msg":"<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2007104/org/1577b70a8423eb46c6a0fd1583dcae31.jpg/0dPWrkZqTqih6jsD5NVjXHPsshlU5nNxBHIvwgRyL8I\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2007104%2Forg%2F1577b70a8423eb46c6a0fd1583dcae31.jpg%2F0dPWrkZqTqih6jsD5NVjXHPsshlU5nNxBHIvwgRyL8I&h=7d2075d3&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人有嗜好很平常，或會累積一大堆收藏品，可是男人的心頭好不時都會成為另一半的「敵人」。近日有女子在二手拍賣網站出售男朋友珍藏的高達模型、四驅車及變型金剛，稱是「幫男友放血」，結果引來大量網民批評，稱「做你男朋友真係喊三聲」，又認為被放血的男友應該與女友分手。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006958/org/f6e375ac4482d1f31bab74ad05d79b6c.jpg/vEHL7TKYtSzY_n8aPxH_UwMJ7YoFDZ6zfBXVD3wV1Q8?v=w1280\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006958%2Forg%2Ff6e375ac4482d1f31bab74ad05d79b6c.jpg%2FvEHL7TKYtSzY_n8aPxH_UwMJ7YoFDZ6zfBXVD3wV1Q8%3Fv%3Dw1280&h=dd592f79&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有女友在網上出售男友的珍藏，圖中所有高達模型叫價499元。（旋轉拍賣網站圖片）<br />\n<br />\n近日在二手拍賣網站「旋轉拍賣 Carousell」上，有女子上載3個出售項目，指要「幫男友放血」。她在內容介紹上提到，出售的東西全部都是珍藏，保存狀況良好，只是男朋友希望騰出空間存放Lego，所以才叫她放售。她又提到不希望有太多舊玩具留在家中，所以請網民「有意買就幫幫手」，更稱如果在星期六交收，「佢（男朋友）都會在場」。<br />\n<br />\n女友出售的男友珍藏包括叫價499元的7隻高達模型連配件、叫價349元的7部四驅車連工具箱及150元的變形金剛模型。<br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006981/org/483d6e9a851d4b88ccf7c11cc63c75be.jpg/vz-BfGHv4jMym0BKGI1_7hefYmtn1oTDq28GOatvBjk\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006981%2Forg%2F483d6e9a851d4b88ccf7c11cc63c75be.jpg%2Fvz-BfGHv4jMym0BKGI1_7hefYmtn1oTDq28GOatvBjk&h=abfd8f84&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006982/org/9e9b1c0719330685cc60c4e7b780a809.jpg/Tayo0bv_4UDraw4oNDbGPWCj8MrbQfMdZ34V_Gd-Ffw\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006982%2Forg%2F9e9b1c0719330685cc60c4e7b780a809.jpg%2FTayo0bv_4UDraw4oNDbGPWCj8MrbQfMdZ34V_Gd-Ffw&h=2f9b22d6&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006983/org/7675e721d231cbe122fd754da027ed95.png/K-6ViteD02IqxzaLvTsDLqW_-Nh_wp5i3SbpB90m6Qc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006983%2Forg%2F7675e721d231cbe122fd754da027ed95.png%2FK-6ViteD02IqxzaLvTsDLqW_-Nh_wp5i3SbpB90m6Qc&h=b58c8bba&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006985/org/fede3efb2628c08ae71a43494d73124f.jpg/3Sa0EV7cLU0HeaiuQpLhUASyLRauqsYYTiPdX04j3V8\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006985%2Forg%2Ffede3efb2628c08ae71a43494d73124f.jpg%2F3Sa0EV7cLU0HeaiuQpLhUASyLRauqsYYTiPdX04j3V8&h=e715c3ef&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006984/org/59d8fd952a7cabf7218a5a2ad7f4a311.png/NWOGQTdoNDZZmLwXoylKEww2xljBbkiHRmhYhkZoWIY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006984%2Forg%2F59d8fd952a7cabf7218a5a2ad7f4a311.png%2FNWOGQTdoNDZZmLwXoylKEww2xljBbkiHRmhYhkZoWIY&h=92e2283e&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006992/org/0f22f4937ef2ec845abefe2b5c2d6237.jpg/cqoXJ0E04zyvigiOR2IOeq54kNU5sO2wOq-4djqvuHY\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006992%2Forg%2F0f22f4937ef2ec845abefe2b5c2d6237.jpg%2FcqoXJ0E04zyvigiOR2IOeq54kNU5sO2wOq-4djqvuHY&h=80f5c1e2&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2006991/org/69ddffc19c3b433b409f1b2a08eddc62.png/SBUOve3zcN2-JPzRYiLobhulcZ2quHP2BF8nLQRfJy0\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2006991%2Forg%2F69ddffc19c3b433b409f1b2a08eddc62.png%2FSBUOve3zcN2-JPzRYiLobhulcZ2quHP2BF8nLQRfJy0&h=200387dc&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2007036/org/4cc04bc835d91dc3e59e85e124e5c4f9.png/76i9yLE158gUIT81fvYJeNlcPbPQ-8QwN3_xRDd_8UQ\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2007036%2Forg%2F4cc04bc835d91dc3e59e85e124e5c4f9.png%2F76i9yLE158gUIT81fvYJeNlcPbPQ-8QwN3_xRDd_8UQ&h=52a60f57&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2007058/org/7d44df7a83443318519502205da4f25e.png/x3QDpBKIMl8xzMcJ8g_P-Ifs_ZrXV3Y9MtUCvjLVAr4\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2007058%2Forg%2F7d44df7a83443318519502205da4f25e.png%2Fx3QDpBKIMl8xzMcJ8g_P-Ifs_ZrXV3Y9MtUCvjLVAr4&h=c876ed69&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2007062/org/9849db32d8e19bd8dd61679d71f0b6ef.png/siuhV7u6Jm6wxYL81nhQ3EwwZSJ1gOOJ86VIEvOlSBI\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2007062%2Forg%2F9849db32d8e19bd8dd61679d71f0b6ef.png%2FsiuhV7u6Jm6wxYL81nhQ3EwwZSJ1gOOJ86VIEvOlSBI&h=0d52da7c&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2007060/org/51a4e620cf710c85267ace55ac871aee.png/iS0X3p53k98zhX87LumMI1HbsokheKcBezRHzXs0R80\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2007060%2Forg%2F51a4e620cf710c85267ace55ac871aee.png%2FiS0X3p53k98zhX87LumMI1HbsokheKcBezRHzXs0R80&h=51c6c3d4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2007059/org/7607feafc7a197b3815f5d5557ee7611.png/4yMMhOJ2zHY1pCns4srs1g5hmMQcBYAX-zDwl_sw8Jc\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2007059%2Forg%2F7607feafc7a197b3815f5d5557ee7611.png%2F4yMMhOJ2zHY1pCns4srs1g5hmMQcBYAX-zDwl_sw8Jc&h=1da09fe4&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<img src=\"https://cdn.hk01.com/di/media/images/2007061/org/68d1a1ba2e65b8129caf2d956a872873.png/pIPbKG7-cF8a5_ssYwFN2FqEAVnSmcP7uuqEerrqhHo\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fcdn.hk01.com%2Fdi%2Fmedia%2Fimages%2F2007061%2Forg%2F68d1a1ba2e65b8129caf2d956a872873.png%2FpIPbKG7-cF8a5_ssYwFN2FqEAVnSmcP7uuqEerrqhHo&h=33bfdb48&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n有網民留言指女友的放血行為有問題，應尊重男友的收藏嗜好。（旋轉拍賣網站截圖）<br />\n<br />\n放血行為引來大量網民批評，直指「做你男朋友真係喊三聲」、「放過你男朋友喇」、「你男朋友有你呢種女朋友真係慘」。另外更有網民表示，即使自己同樣是女性「都嬲到要留言」，因為男友的收藏賣出去之後未必可以買回來，勸女友將心比己，「我係你條仔我都會賣晒你啲袋鞋衫」。<br />\n<br />\n面對網民的指控，女朋友曾回應「佢知道㗎，佢主動叫我放出嚟，要留位畀Lego」。不過網民並不相信女友的回應，稱「畀得你放會Set咁嘅價？」、「呢個價位，我驚淨係回到一隻嘅本／回唔到（本）」。<br />\n<br />\n網民認為被放血的男友十分可憐，建議他盡快分手，亦呼籲其他網民「放呢位師兄一條生路」，不要買「放血產品」，同時提醒女朋友「停一停，諗一諗，小心放走埋男朋友」。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/250471/%E7%A8%B1%E7%95%99%E4%BD%8D%E6%94%BElego-%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E9%AB%98%E9%81%94%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E5%9B%9B%E9%A9%85%E8%BB%8A-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E7%95%99%E6%A2%9D%E7%94%9F%E8%B7%AF\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fwww.hk01.com%2F%25E7%2586%25B1%25E7%2588%2586%25E8%25A9%25B1%25E9%25A1%258C%2F250471%2F%25E7%25A8%25B1%25E7%2595%2599%25E4%25BD%258D%25E6%2594%25BElego-%25E5%25A5%25B3%25E5%258F%258B%25E4%25BB%25A3%25E7%2594%25B7%25E5%258F%258B%25E5%2587%25BA%25E5%2594%25AE%25E9%25AB%2598%25E9%2581%2594%25E6%25A8%25A1%25E5%259E%258B-%25E5%259B%259B%25E9%25A9%2585%25E8%25BB%258A-%25E7%25B6%25B2%25E6%25B0%2591-%25E7%2595%2599%25E6%25A2%259D%25E7%2594%259F%25E8%25B7%25AF&d=mmcIkk46CeecWPKyTqT64CwN645TRhVPBLeqKBQ2Igw%3D&h=e0307800\" target=\"_blank\">https://www.hk01.com/%E7%86%B1%E7%88%86%E8%A9%B1%E9%A1%8C/250471/%E7%A8%B1%E7%95%99%E4%BD%8D%E6%94%BElego-%E5%A5%B3%E5%8F%8B%E4%BB%A3%E7%94%B7%E5%8F%8B%E5%87%BA%E5%94%AE%E9%AB%98%E9%81%94%E6%A8%A1%E5%9E%8B-%E5%9B%9B%E9%A9%85%E8%BB%8A-%E7%B6%B2%E6%B0%91-%E7%95%9